para.example:
To export a nicely-formatted JSON object:

    TheObject theObject = new TheObject();
    DuJson.ExportToLocalFile<TheObject>(theObject, "/Path/To/Export/File");

To export an unformatted JSON object:

    TheObject theObject = new TheObject();
    DuJson.ExportToLocalFile<TheObject>(theObject, "/Path/To/Export/File", false);
